<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>" />

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest" />

    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header><%- include('../partials/header') %></header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-grow">
      <!-- Page Title Section -->
      <section class="bg-gray-100 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center">Storm Damage Insurance Claims Assistance</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600 text-center">Expert guidance through the insurance claim process</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="py-12 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-8">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Navigate Insurance Claims with Confidence</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Dealing with insurance claims after storm damage can be overwhelming and confusing. Maverick Contracting provides expert assistance to help you navigate the entire process, from
                initial documentation to final settlement.
              </p>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Our experienced team works directly with insurance adjusters on your behalf, ensuring that all damage is properly documented and that you receive fair compensation for necessary
                repairs. We understand insurance policies and procedures, and we'll advocate for your best interests every step of the way.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition duration-150">Get Insurance Claim Help</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
              <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Insurance claim assistance" class="w-full h-auto" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Services Section -->
      <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Our Insurance Claim Services</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Service 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-search text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Thorough Damage Assessment</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Comprehensive inspection and documentation of all storm damage to ensure nothing is overlooked in your insurance claim.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-camera text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Detailed Documentation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Professional photo and video documentation of all damage, with detailed reports that satisfy insurance requirements.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-file-signature text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Claim Filing Assistance</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Expert help with completing and submitting all necessary insurance claim forms and documentation correctly and on time.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-user-tie text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Adjuster Meeting Representation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Professional representation during insurance adjuster inspections to ensure all damage is properly identified and documented.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-comments-dollar text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Settlement Negotiation</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Expert negotiation with insurance companies to ensure you receive fair compensation for all necessary repairs and replacements.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Service 6 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <i class="fas fa-tasks text-red-600 text-xl"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Claim Tracking & Management</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Ongoing management of your claim process, including follow-ups with insurance companies and documentation of all communications.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Section -->
      <section class="py-12 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Our Insurance Claim Process</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-12">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">1</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Free Damage Assessment</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">We conduct a thorough inspection of your property to identify all storm damage that may be covered by your insurance policy.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">2</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Documentation & Evidence Collection</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">We gather comprehensive documentation, including photos, videos, and detailed notes of all damage to support your insurance claim.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Claim Filing Assistance</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">We help you file your insurance claim correctly, ensuring all necessary documentation is included and deadlines are met.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Adjuster Meeting Coordination</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">We schedule and attend the insurance adjuster inspection, ensuring all damage is properly identified and documented.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 5 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">5</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Estimate Review & Negotiation</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">We review the insurance company's estimate and negotiate on your behalf if it doesn't adequately cover all necessary repairs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 6 -->
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-red-600 text-white">
                  <span class="text-lg font-bold">6</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Quality Repairs & Restoration</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">
                  Once your claim is approved, we complete all repairs and restoration work to the highest standards, ensuring your property is fully restored.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Question 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Will filing a claim increase my insurance premiums?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Insurance premiums may increase after filing a claim, but this depends on many factors including your policy, claim history, and the nature of the damage. Storm damage is typically
                  considered an "Act of God" and may not impact your rates as significantly as other types of claims. We can discuss your specific situation during your consultation.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long do I have to file a storm damage claim?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Most insurance policies have a time limit for filing claims after damage occurs, typically ranging from one to two years. However, it's best to file as soon as possible after the
                  damage is discovered. Waiting too long can make it more difficult to prove the damage was caused by a specific storm event.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if my insurance claim is denied?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  If your claim is denied, we can help you understand the reason for the denial and explore options for appealing the decision. This may include gathering additional documentation,
                  requesting a re-inspection, or filing a formal appeal. Our experienced team has successfully helped many homeowners overturn initial claim denials.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I have to pay a deductible?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Yes, most insurance policies require you to pay a deductible before coverage begins. The amount varies depending on your policy. We can help you understand your deductible and how it
                  affects your out-of-pocket costs for repairs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <section class="py-12 bg-red-600">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Get Expert Insurance Claim Assistance</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white mb-8">Don't navigate the complex insurance claim process alone. Let our experienced team help you get the compensation you deserve.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
            <a href="tel:612-472-2294" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-white text-red-600 font-bold rounded-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-150">
              <i class="fas fa-phone mr-2"></i> Call (612) 472-2294
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-150">
              <i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i> Schedule a Consultation
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-8 mt-10"><%- include('../partials/footer') %></footer>

    <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
